Introduction

YuBin is a South Korean dancer, singer, and model under MODHAUS.

In 2017-2018, YuBin participated in the Junior Cooking Show "I am Chef". She made it into the final Top 3 contestants on the show.

YuBin was introduced as the eighth member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS on September 9, 2022. She first debuted with the sub-unit Acid Angel from Asia on October 28, 2022, with the mini album "ACCESS". With their first ten revealed members, tripleS debuted on February 13, 2023, with the mini album "ASSEMBLE".

As a member of tripleS, YuBin was placed in the sub-units Acid Angel from Asia, ACID EYES, LOVElution, and Visionary Vision.
